    "home":{
        "brief_story":"To claim the one and only supreme throne, countless rival factions wage war upon this land.",
        "how_to_play":"How to Play",
        "brief_tutorial":"Expend your action points to summon fierce warriors, lead them in battle, or draw mighty cards. Combine their strengths and shatter every obstacle that stands before you.",
